dana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">3.3k</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":3312,\"repo\":\"accurics/terrascan\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - <em>Accurics</em> - Detect compliance and security violations across Infrastructure as Code to mitigate risk before provisioning cloud native infrastructure.</li>","updatedAt":"2022-02-07T13:52:03.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"eozer/awesome-snmp","categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools</h2><h3>CLIs</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.ibr.cs.tu-bs.de/projects/libsmi/\">libsmi tools</a> - Applications built on top of libsmi and an sh/awk script that are integrated with the libsmi distribution.\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.ibr.cs.tu-bs.de/projects/libsmi/smilint.html\">smilint</a> - This is used to check MIB or PIB modules for syntax errors and semantics at some degree. SMIv1/v2 style MIB modules as well as SPPI PIB modules are supported.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.ibr.cs.tu-bs.de/projects/libsmi/smidump.html\">smidump</a> - This is a MIB/PIB compiler. It allows to dump the contents of a module in various formats: SMIv1, SMIv2, SMIng, SPPI, Import Trees, Type Definition Trees, OID Node Trees, MOSY Style, and CORBA IDL definitions according to the JIDM Specs, and others.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.ibr.cs.tu-bs.de/projects/libsmi/smidiff.html\">smidiff</a> - This is a tool that parses two revisions of a MIB module and analyzes the modifications from the old to the new revision.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.ibr.cs.tu-bs.de/projects/libsmi/smiquery.html\">smiquery</a> - This is a MIB/PIB query front end. It can be used to query single items from the command line.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.ibr.cs.tu-bs.de/projects/libsmi/smistrip.html\">smistrip</a> - This is a simple shell/awk script that allows to extract MIB and PIB modules from documents, such as RFCs or Internet Drafts.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>","updatedAt":"2022-02-07T11:40:58.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"eozer/awesome-snmp","categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools</h2><h3>GUIs</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.paessler.com/tools/snmptester\">paessler/snmptester</a> - This tool enables you to debug SNMP activities to find communication and/or data issues in SNMP monitoring configurations. Windows.</li>","updatedAt":"2022-02-07T11:20:17.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"manuzhang/awesome-streaming","categoryHTML":"<h2>Website</h2><h3>Data Pipeline</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/apache/rocketmq\">Apache RocketMQ</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/apache/rocketmq\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">18.2k</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":18215,\"repo\":\"apache/rocketmq\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> [Java] - distributed messaging and streaming platform with low latency, high performance and reliability, trillion-level capacity and flexible scalability.</li>","updatedAt":"2022-02-07T07:49:39.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"davidsonfellipe/awesome-wpo","categoryHTML":"<h1>Application Performance Monitoring</h1>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.datadoghq.com/product/apm/\">Datadog APM</a> - End-to-end distributed tracing and APM at scale, correlated to all telemetry.</li>","updatedAt":"2022-02-07T02:43:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"davidsonfellipe/awesome-wpo","categoryHTML":"<h1>Application Performance Monitoring</h1>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://betteruptime.com\">BetterUptime</a> - A good website monitoring tool (bundling status page, incident notification)</li>","updatedAt":"2022-02-07T02:43:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"davidsonfellipe/awesome-wpo","categoryHTML":"<h1>Application Performance Monitoring</h1>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://nodown.io\">Nodown</a> - Also, a monitoring tool, but that focuses on feature testing</li>","updatedAt":"2022-02-07T02:43:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"davidsonfellipe/awesome-wpo","categoryHTML":"<h1>Application Performance Monitoring</h1>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://pingdom.com\">Pingdom</a> - A tool to get the uptime of your website (with probes from different locations)</li>","updatedAt":"2022-02-07T02:39:44.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"davidsonfellipe/awesome-wpo","categoryHTML":"<h1>Application Performance Monitoring</h1>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://uptimerobot.com\">UptimeRobot</a> - Another uptime monitoring tool (with a generous free plan)</li>","updatedAt":"2022-02-07T02:39:44.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"jaywcjlove/awesome-mac","categoryHTML":"<h2>Communication</h2><h4>Collaboration and Team Tools</h4>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.larksuite.com/en_us/\">Lark</a> - The Next-Gen Collaboration Suite. All your chats, meetings, calendars, docs, and emails in one place. <img src=\"https://jaywcjlove.github.io/sb/ico/min-free.svg\" alt=\"Freeware\" title=\"Freeware\"></li>","updatedAt":"2022-02-07T02:08:39.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"jaywcjlove/awesome-mac","categoryHTML":"<h2>Design and Product</h2><h4>Screencapturing Software</h4>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://shottr.cc/\">Shottr</a> - Screen capture application with features like Scrolling capture, OCR and markup. <img src=\"https://jaywcjlove.github.io/sb/ico/min-free.svg\" alt=\"Freeware\" title=\"Freeware\"></li>","updatedAt":"202